{
  "texts": [
    "Towards Automated Generation and Evaluation of Questions in Educational Domains.",
    "To evaluate the relevance of the key concepts reflected in the development of questions asked by humans and by GPT-3, based on learning materials stemming from a text in an introductory course in data science.",
    "The questions were classified as useful or not useful for learning, with two different focuses: automatic labeling by GPT-3, and manual labeling by expert human judges.",
    "The results showed that the questions generated were favorably rated by all the evaluation methods.",
    "Breakfast with Confucius, Dinner with Lem."
  ]
}